OdiSendMail "-MAILHOST=#BEDIAN.V_MAILING_SERVER" "-PORT=#BEDIAN.V_MAILING_PORT" "-PROTOCOL=smtp" "-AUTH=NO" "-FROM=do_not_reply@itzbund.de" "-SUBJECT=[BEDIAN ""<%=odiRef.getContext( ""CTX_NAME"" )%>""] Ladelauf erfolgreich abgeschlossen" "-TO=#BEDIAN.V_MAILING_STATUS_EMPFAENGER" Der Lade-Prozess BEDIAN auf der Umgebung "<%=odiRef.getContext( "CTX_NAME" )%>" ist erfolgreich durchgelaufen.
Session_Nummer: "<%=odiRef.getSession( "SESS_GUID" )%>"
Folgende Daten wurden in den einzelnen Schichten verarbeitet:
#BEDIAN.V_MAILING_STATUS_ERGEBNIS
SELECT CHAR_VALUE FROM <?=odiRef.getSchemaName("DWH_MTD", "D") ?>.ETL_CONFIGURATION WHERE PROCESS_NAME = 'BEDIAN' AND CONFIGURATION = 'Statusmail_Aktivierung'
SELECT CHAR_VALUE FROM <?=odiRef.getSchemaName("DWH_MTD", "D") ?>.ETL_CONFIGURATION WHERE PROCESS_NAME = 'ALLGEMEIN' AND CONFIGURATION = 'Mailserver'
SELECT NUMBER_VALUE FROM <?=odiRef.getSchemaName("DWH_MTD", "D") ?>.ETL_CONFIGURATION WHERE PROCESS_NAME = 'ALLGEMEIN' AND CONFIGURATION = 'Mailserver'
SELECT CHAR_VALUE FROM <?=odiRef.getSchemaName("DWH_MTD", "D") ?>.ETL_CONFIGURATION WHERE PROCESS_NAME = 'BEDIAN' AND CONFIGURATION = 'Statusmail_Empfaenger'

Select listagg(text, chr(13)) WITHIN GROUP (order by start_date) ergebnis from ( select rpad(load_plan_name || ' (' || sess_keywords || '): ',40) || chr(9) || to_char(anz,'999G999G999')|| ' verarbeitete Datenstze [' || to_char(start_date,'DD.MM.YYYY HH24:MI:SS') || '->' || to_char(end_date,'DD.MM.YYYY HH24:MI:SS') || ']' text, start_date from ( select lp.load_plan_name, st.sess_keywords , lp.start_date, lp.end_date, round(lp.DURATION/60,2) minuten, sum(nb_ins + nb_upd + nb_del) anz from ODIEBIV_ODI_REPO.snp_lpi_run lp join ( select task_beg, task_end, substr(to_char(regexp_substr(def_txt, '-LOAD_PLAN_NAME=[^"]*')),17) load_plan from ODIEBIV_ODI_REPO.snp_sess_task_log where sess_no = (select parent_sess_no from ODIEBIV_ODI_REPO.snp_session where global_id = '<?=odiRef.getSession("SESS_GUID") ?>' ) ) ses on lp.load_plan_name = ses.load_plan and lp.start_date between ses.task_beg and ses.task_end JOIN ODIEBIV_ODI_REPO.snp_lpi_step_log st on lp.i_lp_inst = st.i_lp_inst group by lp.load_plan_name, lp.start_date, lp.end_date, lp.DURATION, st.sess_keywords ) )
